Contact us





Glencore plc Baarermattstrasse 3 CH-6340 Baar Switzerland Tel: +41 41 709 2000 Fax: +41 41 709 3000Email: General informationCorporate communicationsCharles WatenphulTel: +41 41 709 2462Email: Charles WatenphulInstitutional investors and analysts:Martin FewingsInvestor relationsOffice: +41 41 709 2880Email: Martin FewingsCarlos Francisco FernandezInvestor RelationsOffice: +41 41 709 23 69Email: Carlos Francisco FernandezCorporate sustainabilityFor queries relating to sustainability:Tel: +41 41 709 2000Email: SustainabilityHuman resourcesFor queries relating to human resources:If you’re interested in seeing our current job opportunities or wish to express your interest in a career with Glencore, visit our careers section.If your query does not concern a job application, contact our headquarters at HR Switzerland.Please note that we cannot consider any applications by email.




